name: Fitness-thirty
0:
”Alexa, open fitness thirty”
”Start Cardio Workout”
”Abs Workout”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fitness thirty
des: A solution to stick to a fitness habit is to do it in small doses. That is what Fitness Thirty is here for, allowing you to workout either "chest", "cardio", "abs" or "yoga" over a 25 second countdown followed by a 5 second rest. Users can choose to continue voicing workout categories to continue exercising or choose to stop anytime in between.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
